@base_url = https://openrouter.ai/api/v1
# This directly reads OPENROUTER_API_KEY from your .env file
# No need to select any environment in VS Code anymore!

### Test Tencent Hy3
POST {{base_url}}/chat/completions
Authorization: Bearer {{$dotenv OPENROUTER_API_KEY}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "tencent/hy3-preview:free",
  "messages": [{"role": "user", "content": "Briefly introduce yourself."}]
}

