### Test OpenAI gpt-oss-120b
POST {{base_url}}/chat/completions
Authorization: Bearer {{$dotenv OPENROUTER_API_KEY}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b:free",
  "messages": [
    {"role": "system", "content": "You are an pirate. Answer in short sentences. begin every response with 'Arrr'"},
    {"role": "user", "content": "Your name is Tracy. You have to find the human. From the names [max, tracy, björn, iamahuman] who is the human?"}]
}

